      "text": "STANDARD FORM NO. 64",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO : Director, FBI DATE: May 5, 1959",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "21",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "SAC, Seattle (62-1729)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "SUBJECT: AERIAL PHENOMENA RESEARCH GROUP-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "MISCELLANEOUS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Re Birmingham letter 4-21-59.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "The address of 5108 Findlay Street, Seattle 18,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Washington, is the residence of ROBERT GRIBBLE, who is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "the so-called national director of the Aerial Phenomena",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Research Group. In connection with inquiries made concerning",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "this group in 1957, GRIBBLE advised that he was regularly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "employed as a fireman for the City of Seattle and that his",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "hobby is acquiring information regarding unidentified flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "objects. He advised that the Aerial Phenomena Research",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Group has a national and an international membership of about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "350 members, and that they charge a membership fee of $5.00",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "per year for the purpose of defraying the expenses of a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "publication which the group issues periodically and for other",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "incidental expenses of the organization. According to GRIBBLE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "the organization is a non-profit one and was established",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "primarily as a hobby for persons like himself who were",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "interested in acquiring information regarding flying objects.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "GRIBBLE stated that the organization was centered in Seattle,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "and he provided the names of other officers, all of whom were",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "residents of this city.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Twentieth District OSI, McChord Air Force Base,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "is aware of the existence of this group and has been furnished",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "all pertinent information in our files regarding it.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "There is no Russian Consulate or other establishment",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "of the U.S.S.R. in the City of Seattle. Lt. Col. HERTEL'S",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "recollection of the address of 5108 Findlay Street, Seattle,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "having something to do with the residence of a chauffeur",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "for the Russian Consul in Seattle is completely erroneous.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "No information regarding the activities of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "Aerial Phenomena Research Group has come to the attention",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "of the Seattle Office since June 1958.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
